#: ../../index.md:6
#: c47aa6a86d0641948214682ae4c5eb05
msgid "[MappingTool](mapping.md) provides a mapping configuration from csv timeseries to network. This configuration allows to generate iidm network at specified times. Furthermore, it allows using the second tool, MetrixTool."
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.md:10
#: e1af0f03f744416393f2db4933045a27
msgid "[MetrixTool](metrix.md) can compute power load flow and optimal power load flow for the multi variant networks generated by the mapping tool. Its outputs are completed by synthesis."
msgstr ""

#: ../../index.md:13
#: 90b49394b90d46cdab4fb75b69a7ec6b
msgid "MetrixTool calls *[metrix simulator](metrix-simulator.md)* as an external program. This program has its own requirements."
msgstr ""

